Google Groups are the default type of group and have a label with a key of `cloudidentity.googleapis.com/groups.discussion_forum` and an empty value. Existing Google Groups can have an additional label with a key of `cloudidentity.googleapis.com/groups.security` and an empty value added to them. **This is an immutable change and the security label cannot be removed once added.** Dynamic groups have a label with a key of `cloudidentity.googleapis.com/groups.dynamic`. Identity-mapped groups for Cloud Search have a label with a key of `system/groups/external` and an empty value.
